<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>Error</title>
<style type="text/css">
body {
    background-color: #eee;
    font-family: "微软雅黑", "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, "宋体", sans-serif;
}
.container {
    width: 800px;
    height: 600px;
    border: 1px #ebeaea solid;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    margin: -300px 0 0 -400px;
    background-color: #fff;
}
.banner {
    width: 800px;
    height: 230px;
    background-image: url("data:image/png;base64,");
}
.message, .reason, .foot {
    text-align: center;
}
.message {
    font-size: 40px;
    line-height: 40px;
    margin-top: 30px;
    color: #000;
}
.reason {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-top: 25px;
    color: #a5a5a5;
}
.report {
    margin-top: 80px;
    text-align: center;
}
.foot {
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 90px;
}
.button {
	color:#fff;
	background-color:#2fabf8;
	border-color:#2798e0;
	font-weight:300;
	font-size:16px;
	text-decoration:none;
	text-align:center;
	line-height:40px;
	height:40px;
	padding:0 40px;
	margin:0;
	display:inline-block;
	appearance:none;
	cursor:pointer;
	border:none;
	-webkit-box-sizing:border-box;
	-moz-box-sizing:border-box;
	box-sizing:border-box;
	-webkit-transition-property:all;
	transition-property:all;
	-webkit-transition-duration:.3s;
	transition-duration:.3s;
}
.button:hover,.button:focus {
	background-color:#1897e5;
	text-decoration:none;
	outline:none;
}
.button-glow {
	-webkit-animation-duration:3s;
	animation-duration:3s;
	-webkit-animation-iteration-count:infinite;
	animation-iteration-count:infinite;
	-webkit-animation-name:glowing;
	animation-name:glowing;
}
.button-rounded {
	border-radius:4px;
}
#submit {
    visibility: hidden;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="banner"></div>
    <div class="message">您浏览的网页暂时无法显示</div>
    <div class="reason">可能地址存在错误，或者网页已被删除</div>
    <div class="report">
        <form action="#report" method="post" style="display:none">
            <input type="hidden" value="#" id="url" name="url" />
            <input type="hidden" value="" id="ts" name="ts" />
        </form>
        <a id="submit" href="javascript:void(0)" class="button button-glow button-rounded">报告该问题</a>
    </div>
    <div class="foot">&copy; 2016 安恒玄武盾</div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        document.getElementById("ts").value = Math.round((new Date()).getTime()/1000);
        document.getElementById("submit").onclick = function() {
            document.getElementById("url").value = window.location.href;
            alert("url is: " + document.getElementById("url").value);
            document.getElementsByTagName("FORM")[0].submit();
        };
    </script>
</div>
</body>
</html>
